\end_inset

 אמ
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

מ 
\begin_inset Formula $m\ge n$
\end_inset

 וגם לכל 
\begin_inset Formula $1\le i\le n$
\end_inset

 מתקיים 
\begin_inset Formula $a_{i}=b_{i}$
\end_inset

.
