\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Formula $\le_{\text{pre}}$
\end_inset

 אנטי-סימטרי חלש:
 תהיינה 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(a_{i}\right)_{i=1}^{n},\left(b_{i}\right)_{i=1}^{m}\in A^{\ast}$
\end_inset

 כך ש-
\begin_inset Formula $\left(a_{i}\right)_{i=1}^{n}\le_{\text{pre}}\left(b_{i}\right)_{i=1}^{m}$
\end_inset

 וגם 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(b_{i}\right)_{i=1}^{m}\le_{\text{pre}}\left(a_{i}\right)_{i=1}^{n}$
\end_inset

.
 אזי 
\begin_inset Formula $m\ge n$
\end_inset

 וגם 
\begin_inset Formula $n\ge m$
\end_inset

,
